Q4:
The largest value I tried where is still work correctly is 2147483647.
When I try 2147483648 or larger, it has compile error: Exception in thread "main" java.util.InputMismatchException: For input string: "2147483648"
2147483648 is the largest number an integer can represent, so the compile error occurs.
